org.apache.sysds.runtime.privacy

Class PrivacyConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.sysds.runtime.privacy.PrivacyConstraint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class PrivacyConstraint
extends Object
implements Externalizable
    PrivacyConstraint holds all privacy constraints for data in the system at compile time and runtime.
